            <section ID="LINK_fe1a2839-00d8-4525-b13d-1a9aa5cfb459">
               <id root="2c6e7822-d15c-4360-b211-13e02efe71f2"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="bold">DESCRIPTION</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Each mL contains: Indigotindisulfonate Sodium 8 mg, Water for Injection q.s. pH adjusted, when necessary, with Citric Acid and/or Sodium Citrate. Sterile, nonpyrogenic.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Sufficient Indigo Carmine is contained in each 5 mL ampule to permit accurate withdrawal and administration of the full dose. It gives a deep blue solution when dissolved in water.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>The structural formula is:</paragraph>
                  <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1"/>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20191206"/>
               <component>
                  <observationMedia ID="MM1">
